value.0: I will answer, though I find your words very... I guess I find your speech very modern. The Lords would probably help you better than I.
Just go talk to the Lords. They'll listen to your stories. You have so many... like Quint did... Things like that bring change...
I can't say any more. People tell too many stories. People want too many things. Like that Quint.
The guard? At the castle gate? I... I don't remember... He's new here... He protects us from... from change...
What goes on in Castle Jhareg is not to be spoken of. It might bring change, and nobody wants that.
You don't understand. The telling of tales will lead only to trouble - just ask anyone!
